data.title: Wikipedia Co-Founder Refuses to Comply With China’s Censorship "Wales said he would rather have no Wikipedia in China than comply with any form of censorship. Wikipedia will always refuse to comply with Gov't requests to restrict information, calling access to knowledge and education a human right."
